Text: "First, I never left Brazil, and I am studying English to be able to specialize\
  \ in languages \u200B\u200Band have more access to other countries and cultures.\
  \ I've been locked up for a wedding and now finally divorcing myself, I've changed\
  \ my life. I'm heading in the other direction, planning a future and this happens\
  \ through trips around the world, no matter which country. I intend to do this a\
  \ way of life and make money."
